metadata.description:
The world of SYLTARE began with the simultaneous resonance of several universes made of SYL due to ‘strokes’.
In the early days of discord, people who made the game stable in the early universe and consistently cheered with harsh words were called tuners.
We would like to dedicate this medal to our “tuners” who always help us to make a perfect harmony, even though it is still incomplete.
metadata.name: SYLTARE, Tuner of The Universe #2
